---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const title = "Our Solutions";
const subTitle =
    "From the factory floor to the finance office. We re-engineer your workflows for speed and accuracy.";
---

<MainLayout title={title}>
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white">{title}</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
            {subTitle}
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-14">
        <!-- Section 1: Business Process Automation (The Core) -->
        <div class="mb-10 lg:mb-14">
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-4xl md:leading-tight dark:text-white"
            >
                Business Process Automation (The Core)
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                At the heart of every efficient organization is a robust
                mechanism for handling information.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-24 grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
                <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                    We implement <strong>Frappe/ERPNext</strong> to re-engineer how
                    your business moves. This isn't just about installing software;
                    it’s about architecting a better way to work.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    We map your complex procurement, inventory, and financial
                    workflows and digitize them. No more walking papers from
                    desk to desk for signatures. We configure dynamic approval
                    request systems where a Purchase Order generated in the
                    warehouse is instantly visible to the CFO for approval,
                    budget checked against real-time ledgers.
                </p>
                <ul
                    class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400"
                >
                    <li>
                        <strong>Financial Tracking:</strong> Automated ledgers that
                        update the moment a transaction happens.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>HR & Payroll:</strong> Seamless management of your
                        workforce, compliant with Ugandan tax laws.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Supply Chain:</strong> End-to-end visibility from
                        purchase request to goods receipt.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div
                class="rounded-xl border border-yellow-100 bg-yellow-50 p-8 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-neutral-900/50"
            >
                <!-- Placeholder for ERP visual or Icon -->
                <h3
                    class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400"
                >
                    ERPNext Implementation
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    Centralized control for Finances, HR, and Operations.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2: Industrial Integration (The Data Source) -->
        <div class="mb-24 grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div
                class="order-2 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-8 lg:order-1 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-neutral-900/50"
            >
                <h3
                    class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-neutral-800 dark:text-yellow-400"
                >
                    Ignition SCADA
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    Real-time data from PLCs and Sensors.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">
                    Industrial Integration (The Data Source)
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                    A business process is only as good as the data feeding it.
                    In manufacturing and heavy industry, that data lives in PLCs
                    and sensors, not on keyboards.
                </p>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    We use <strong>Ignition SCADA</strong> to tap directly into your
                    Operational Technology. We connect to your plant floor to monitor
                    run-times, downtimes, and production counts automatically. This
                    "OT to IT" bridge ensures that your ERP isn't just guessing based
                    on end-of-day reports—it knows exactly what was produced, when,
                    and at what cost.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 3: Custom Development & Payments (The Edge) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
                <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl dark:text-white">
                    Custom Development & Payments (The Edge)
                </h2>
                <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">
                    Sometimes, off-the-shelf solutions leave a 10% gap that
                    causes 90% of the friction. We write custom <strong
                        >Python</strong
                    > code to bridge that gap.
                </p>
                <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    Whether you need a specialized vendor portal, a custom
                    logistics tracker, or a unique customer-facing app, we build
                    it to fit your exact ecosystem. Crucially, we integrate <strong
                        >Mobile Money (M-Pesa, Airtel)</strong
                    > and local bank APIs directly into your system. Automate disbursements
                    to casual workers or reconcile incoming payments instantly without
                    manual bank statement analysis.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="rounded-xl border border-yellow-100 bg-yellow-50 p-8 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-neutral-900/50"
            >
                <h3
                    class="mb-4 text-xl font-bold text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400"
                >
                    Python & Fintech Integrations
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    Custom portals and Mobile Money bridges.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</MainLayout>
